BuildRequires:  pkgconfig(gsl)
BuildRequires:  pkgconfig(lal) >= 7.2.0
BuildRequires:  pkgconfig(lalframe) >= 2.0.0
BuildRequires:  pkgconfig(lalinference) >= 4.0.0
BuildRequires:  pkgconfig(lalsimulation) >= 4.0.0
